141
00:18:23,119 --> 00:18:27,839
[SPEAKER_01] Malo smo pričali o tom prometu, o kako on to doživljava, znaš.

142
00:18:28,799 --> 00:18:31,839
[SPEAKER_01] I vratio se mirno natrag u centar.

143
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:37,759
